Order is important here.  Builders progressively replace stage-0 packages with stage-1 replacements.
The replaced version points to in-nix-store sysroot.  Replacement is by redirecting
ELF interpreter and supplying RUNPATH

Dependency Tower

   +-------------------------------------------+
   |               nxfs-toolchain-1            |
   +-------------------------------------------+
   |               nxfs-tar-1                  |
   +-------------------------------------------+
   |               nxfs-coreutils-1            |
   +-------------------------------------------+
   |               nxfs-patchelf-1             |
   +-------------------------------------------+
   |               nxfs-bash-1                 |
   +-------------------------------------------+
   |               nxfs-sysroot-1              |
   +------------------+------------------------+
   | bootstrap-0      | nxfs-redirect-elf-file |
   +------------------+------------------------+
